  "text": "It seems very probable that the effects of HIV on the immune system will also influence the efficacy of treatment, since host immune responses have been shown to enhance the efficacy of several schistosomicidal drugs, including praziquantel. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Possible effects of HIV on praziquantel treatment are important because it is the most widely used drug due to its ease of administration, tolerable side effects, and low cost.",
